article.description: — Noah Gurley had 19 points as Furman rolled past South Carolina State 118-51 on Monday.
article.headline: Gurley, Kenney lift Furman past SC State 118-51
article.linkText: Gurley, Kenney lift Furman past SC State 118-51
article.story: GREENVILLE, S.C. -- — Noah Gurley had 19 points as Furman rolled past South Carolina State 118-51 on Monday. Colin Kenney added 16 points, Jonny Lawrence chipped in 15 and Clay Mounce had 14 points for Furman (6-3). Tariq Simmons had 15 points for the Bulldogs (0-10). Rahsaan Edwards added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
